    <title>Linux下好用的4款ss/ssr客户端</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2019/01/25/linuxssr/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2019/01/25/linuxssr/</id>
    <published>2019-01-25T03:09:54.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-01-26T14:37:25.332Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="写在开头"><a href="#写在开头" class="headerlink" title="写在开头"></a>写在开头</h2><p>在当今的时代，高墙逐渐变厚，大陆人想连接世界变得越来越困难。但是，得益于一些智慧的人群，让我们身处大陆的人也能链接世界。</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="一、Shadowsocks标准客户端"><a href="#一、Shadowsocks标准客户端" class="headerlink" title="一、Shadowsocks标准客户端"></a>一、Shadowsocks标准客户端</h2><p>Shadowsocks项目：<a href="https://github.com/shadowsocks/shadowsocks" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Github</a>相关文档已被删除。但是还是被大部分人保存了下来。Shadowsocks官方linux客户端并没有GUI界面，需要手动编译配置。</p><h3 id="Debian-Ubuntu"><a href="#Debian-Ubuntu" class="headerlink" title="Debian/Ubuntu"></a>Debian/Ubuntu</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">apt-get install python-pip</span><br><span class="line">pip install shadowsocks</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Arch-Linux"><a href="#Arch-Linux" class="headerlink" title="Arch Linux"></a>Arch Linux</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo pacman -S yaourt</span><br><span class="line">yaourt shadowsocks-git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="CentOS"><a href="#CentOS" class="headerlink" title="CentOS"></a>CentOS</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo yum install python-setuptools</span><br><span class="line">easy_install pip</span><br><span class="line">pip install --upgrade pip</span><br><span class="line">sudo pip install shadowsocks</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="二、ShadowsocksR标准客户端"><a href="#二、ShadowsocksR标准客户端" class="headerlink" title="二、ShadowsocksR标准客户端"></a>二、ShadowsocksR标准客户端</h2><p>ShadowsocksR项目：<a href="https://github.com/shadowsocksrr/shadowsocksr-csharp" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Github</a><br>ShadowsocksR官方linux客户端集成了ss的优良传统，也没有GUI界面，仍需手动配置。</p><h3 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/ssrbackup/shadowsocksr</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><p>以下为GUI界面版ss及ssr客户端。</p><h2 id="三、Shadowsocks-Qt5"><a href="#三、Shadowsocks-Qt5" class="headerlink" title="三、Shadowsocks-Qt5"></a>三、Shadowsocks-Qt5</h2><p>这是基于Qt的GUI版Shadowsocks客户端，Github项目：<a href="https://github.com/shadowsocks/shadowsocks-qt5" target="_blank" rel="noopener">点击</a></p><img src="/2019/01/25/linuxssr/ss-qt5.png" title="Shadowsocks-Qt5"><ul><li>Shadowsocks-Qt5是用Qt 5用C ++编写的。</li><li>支持流量统计</li><li>支持服务器延迟（滞后）测试</li><li>同时使用多个配置文件</li></ul><h3 id="CentOS-7"><a href="#CentOS-7" class="headerlink" title="CentOS 7"></a>CentOS 7</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget https://copr.fedorainfracloud.org/coprs/librehat/shadowsocks/repo/epel-7/librehat-shadowsocks-epel-7.repo</span><br><span class="line">sudo mv librehat-shadowsocks-epel-7.repo /etc/yum.repos.d/</span><br><span class="line">sudo yum update</span><br><span class="line">sudo yum install -y shadowsocks-qt5</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Ubuntu"><a href="#Ubuntu" class="headerlink" title="Ubuntu"></a>Ubuntu</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo add-apt-repository ppa:hzwhuang/ss-qt5</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get update</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install shadowsocks-qt5</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Debian"><a href="#Debian" class="headerlink" title="Debian"></a>Debian</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><figcaption><span>安装主要依赖</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-get install python-m2crypto</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install qt5-qmake qtbase5-dev libqrencode-dev libappindicator-dev libzbar-dev libbotan1.10-dev</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plain"><figcaption><span>安装libQtShadowsocks</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/shadowsocks/libQtShadowsocks.git</span><br><span class="line">cd libQtShadowsocks</span><br><span class="line">sudo dpkg-buildpackage -uc -us -b</span><br><span class="line">cd ..</span><br><span class="line">sudo dpkg -i libqtshadowsocks_1.8.0-1_amd64.deb</span><br><span class="line">sudo dpkg -i libqtshadowsocks-dev_1.8.0-1_amd64.deb</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plain"><figcaption><span>安装 shadowsocks-qt5</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd shadowsocks-qt5</span><br><span class="line">sudo dpkg-buildpackage -uc -us -b</span><br><span class="line">cd ..</span><br><span class="line">sudo dpkg -i shadowsocks-qt5_2.6.0-1_amd64.deb</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Arch-Linux-1"><a href="#Arch-Linux-1" class="headerlink" title="Arch Linux"></a>Arch Linux</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo pacman -S yaourt</span><br><span class="line">yaourt shadowsocks-qt5</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="四、electron-ssr"><a href="#四、electron-ssr" class="headerlink" title="四、electron-ssr"></a>四、electron-ssr</h2><p>electron-ssr是一个非常美观的GUI界面SSR客户端，支持订阅等若干高级功能。另外，Appimage文件支持几乎所有Linux发行版，不用考虑依赖问题。</p><img src="/2019/01/25/linuxssr/electron-ssr.png" title="electron-ssr"><p>Github项目：<a href="https://github.com/erguotou520/electron-ssr" target="_blank" rel="noopener">点击</a><br>Appimgage下载：<a href="https://github.com/erguotou520/electron-ssr/releases/download/v0.2.5/electron-ssr-0.2.5.AppImage" target="_blank" rel="noopener">点击</a></p>]]></content>
    
